      "_type": "block",
      "_key": "intro",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Position tolerance is the most powerful and widely used geometric tolerance in GD&T. When combined with material condition modifiers (MMC and LMC), position tolerance provides maximum design flexibility while ensuring functional requirements and enabling efficient manufacturing processes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
